cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.MM

The paper deals with resource allocation in mobile edge computing systems, which involves wireless communication and computing resources. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves optimization and distributed algorithms, which are common in the categories cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with load balancing, which is a common topic in the category cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). Finally, the paper involves mobile computing, which is a topic in the category cs.MM (Multimedia).
